      "content": "Wait, are you saying it's not a violation? I'm looking at the language he used toward that group of fans—it seems pretty targeted and borderline abusive. If we let this stand and it turns into a bigger scandal because we didn't act, that's going to make us look bad. Can you specifically walk me through which part of the policy it *doesn't* break? I need to be 100% sure before I tell the Director we're standing by it.",
